Set Up Git:
git config --global user.name "Your Name"
git config --global user.email "youremail@domain.com"

other commands
git clone (url)  #intial pull request for git repository, wil create a file in current directory of the git repository
git add (file names) #adding new files to git
git commit (file names)  #commiting them to git
git push -u origin main  #pushing new commited files to github

git pull (url)  #pulling any edits or new files made in github
